shion=new_hero
address=res/img/heroi.png
icon=res/img/heroi_icon.png
width=50
height=64
num_row=1
num_col=5
speed=3
space=1
-
EOF

shion is the name of the hero.

new_heroi means that this is a new kind of hero.
end is the address of the image to be loaded
icon is the address of the icon that will be shown on the upper left corner of the screen.
width is the width of the object to be draw.
height is the height of the object to be draw.
num_lin is the number of rows that the animation sprite has.
num_col is the number of columns that the animation sprite has.
speed is the speed that each frame of the animation is shown. (the lower, the faster) // kind of delay
esp is the space between two draws in the sprite